      <meta name="Description"
       Content="The Centre for Policy on Ageing is an is an independent, UK based, research organisation aiming to formulate and promote social policies which will allow all older people to achieve the full potential of their later years. CPA promotes informed debate about issues affecting older age groups, stimulates awareness of the needs of older people and encourages good practice. CPA has its own list of publications on policy issues and maintains an internationally renowned library and information service on the social, behavioural and health aspects of older age. CPA hosts the AgeInfo information service.">
