<tr><td class="quad" colspan="4" ><a href="http://www.spandp.net/" target="_blank"><img src="/images/social_policy_and_practice.jpg" align="left" ></a>The Centre for Policy on Ageing, hosts <a href="http://ageinfo.cpa.org.uk" target="_blank">Ageinfo</a>, the UK's only bibliographic database dedicated to ageing and older age. The Ageinfo data is also available as part of the wider <a href="http://www.ovid.com/site/catalog/databases/1859.jsp?cid=ovid-web-OvidHomepage" target="_blank">Social Policy and Practice</a> database hosted by <a href="http://www.ovid.com/site/catalog/databases/1859.jsp?cid=ovid-web-OvidHomepage" target="_blank">OVID</a>.
