</td></tr><tr><td class="quad" colspan="4"><hr></td></tr>

<tr><td class="quad" colspan="4" ><a href="/images/Independent-Age-Care-Home-Performance-March2017-England.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="/images/Independent-Age-Care-Home-Performance.jpg" align="left" ></a><br>Independent Age has carried out a regional analysis of care home performance in England based on CQC data.
