<tr><td class="quad" colspan="4" ><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-39196579" target="_blank"><img src="/images/budget-2017.jpg" align="left" ></a>The Centre for Policy on Ageing welcomes the &pound;2bn, over 3 years, additional funding for Social Care outlined in the March 8th Budget and looks forward to a long term resolution of the funding issue.
