</td></tr><tr><td class="quad" colspan="4"><hr></td></tr>

<tr><td class="quad" colspan="4" ><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/575797/Baby_boomers_v0.2.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="/images/baby_boomers_fit_for_the_future.jpg" align="left" ></a>The Annual Report of the Chief Medical Officer - <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/575797/Baby_boomers_v0.2.pdf" target="_blank"><i>Baby Boomers: Fit for the Future</i></a>, notes that good' work is good for health and self-esteem and that for older people to work longer may help them to help stay healthy for longer.&nbsp;<br>
