<br>For details of <a href="https://www.kingsfund.org.uk/sites/files/kf/field/field_publication_file/Autumn_Statement_Kings_Fund_Nov_2016_3.pdf" target="_blank">the report</a> and further information see the CPA <a href= "/cpa/policies_on_ageing.html" target="_blank">Policies on Ageing</a> web page.
</td></tr><tr><td class="quad" colspan="4"><hr></td></tr>


<tr><td class="quad" colspan="4" ><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/559943/independent-review-of-the-state-pension-age-interim-report.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="/images/SPA_Review.jpg" align="left" ></a>John Cridland, on behalf of the Department for Work and Pensions, has carried out an independent review of the state pension age and produced an <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/559943/independent-review-of-the-state-pension-age-interim-report.pdf" target="_blank">interim report</a> to which responses are requested by 31st December 2016.&nbsp;<br>
For more information see the CPA <a href= "/cpa/policies_on_ageing.html" target="_blank">Policies on Ageing</a> web page.
